Wrongly convicted of treason on the basis of an anonymous tip to the authorities, you are exiled from your homeland, the Kingdom of Panavera.
You are cast into the wilderness, in which you face many a peril, struggling as you can to survive.
You must make your way back to civilization and clear your name.
To do so, will you wield the pen or the sword?
The choice is yours...

The Wanderer, Chapter 1: The Broken Lands